heading: Entry Desk (8:00 - 9:00 AM)
description: Team members collect their ID cards and team kits at the check-in desk.

heading: Welcome KeyNote & Morning Sessions (9:00 - 12:00 AM)
description: Start the day with a welcome note followed by an insightful speaker session and engaging workshops.

heading: Continue Development (2:00 PM onwards)
description: Resume and progress with ongoing development work.

heading: Session II (3:00 PM - 3:40 PM)
description: Attend a session focused on skill enhancement.

heading: Breakfast (8:00 AM - 9:00 AM)
description: Start the day with a hearty breakfast.

heading: Pitching/Evaluation (10:00 PM onwards)
description: Teams present their projects for evaluation.

heading: Prize Distribution and Closing Note (12:00 PM - 1:00 PM)
description: Receive awards and tokens, followed by a closing note.

heading: Networking (1:00 PM onwards)
description: Connect with peers and wrap up the event with networking.
